window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The companion novel to Rin Chupeco's <i>The Girl from the Well</i>, which <i>Kirkus</i> called a \"Stephen King-like horror story\". </p> <p>After barely escaping the evil spirit that tried to destroy his soul, Tark vows to spend his life protecting the innocent. So when his mentor goes missing on a ghost-hunting expedition, Tark and Okiku join the search. But the Suicide Forest has seduced thousands of people to their deaths over the centuries and is thick with their sorrows. </p> <p>With time running out and danger at every turn, Tark will either become a hero - or die trying. </p>"; 
